org.codice.ddf.migration

Interface MigrationEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<MigrationEntry>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExportMigrationEntry, ImportMigrationEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExportMigrationEntryImpl, ExportMigrationJavaPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, ExportMigrationPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, ExportMigrationSystemPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, ImportMigrationDirectoryEntryImpl, ImportMigrationEmptyEntryImpl, ImportMigrationEntryImpl, ImportMigrationExternalEntryImpl, ImportMigrationJavaPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, ImportMigrationPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, ImportMigrationSystemPropertyReferencedEntryImpl, MigrationEntryImpl

    public interface MigrationEntry
extends Comparable<MigrationEntry>
    The MigrationEntry interface provides support for artifacts that are being exported or imported during migration.

    This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library.
